channel.title: Why can i only log into 10% of servers?
channel.description:
everytime i try log into a server theres like a 10% chance it isnt down even tho it says it is online :confused:
i click on server status look which servers are online, then type them in and 90% of the time their apparently down, even tho it says they are online :confused: need help im comfused.
